HAWKS have bust 33 illegal gold miners in Ellerton
Rehabilitated Mine in Hlaniki village outside Giyani in Limpopo.A disruptive operation by the Hawks’ Serious Organised
Crime Investigation Unit, joined by  the
Department for Mineral Resource (DMR), Provincial Organised Crime Unit, Public
Order Police, the Air Wing and Local Criminal Record Centre cornered the
suspects.HAWKS spokesperson Captain Matimba Maluleke said the
multi-disciplinary operation ensued following an outcry by the local community
about the alleged illegal mining of gold at Ellerton mine that was closed by
